  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to attenuate the systemic inflammatory response after
      Endovascular repair of abdominal aortic aneurysms, by administration of a single preoperative
      dosage of Methylprednisolone.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
